**Play**
`!play` will play the audio from *almost any* link you specify
This command takes a `link` parameter which is the link to the YouTube video, Soundcloud song, Twitch VoD, etc that you wish to play

**You must be connected to a voice channel for this command to work!**

e.g. `!play https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VVggXZPCuYw`
